name: Flores Wonderland Tour
description: FLORES WONDERLAND TOUR is a local travel company based in Labuan Bajo, East Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia. Flores wonderland tour is has committed to help and bridge you to the depth of our wonderland places both in Flores Island and Komodo island and We are professional team and operates legally under Indonesian Tourist Guide Association. Flores wonderland tour focuses in organizing Private Tours to Komodo Island and Flores Island Indonesia either Individual or Group of travelers. Our tour packages offer the travelers a great trip to discover Komodo National Park to see Komodo Dragon and other Wild life, the beauty the nature and under the sea, meanwhile Flores tours will provide trips to explore the highlight of the culture, nature and people of Flores such as, wonderful of Kelimutu Three Colored Lakes, Bena trditional village, Wae Rebo village,Flores culture, caci whip fighting dance, Penti thanks giving ceremony, wonderful beauty of the Nature and so much more

name: Jesha Travel
description: We offer you the perfect opportunity to make a wonderful individual tours on the Island of Flores and Komodo with all the highlights that the island offer. You can take a tour with us for a very attractive prices and are suitable for different target groups; for young and old, from backpacker to luxury lovers. Our tours are tailor-made by local guides with years of experience. On our website we offer various tours through the central part of Flores, Komodo and soon also Lombok and Sumba. We are constantly looking for new, unknown and less tourist destinations. We are thinking out of the box! This makes our tours unique and special.

name: Roland Tour & Travel
